column27: "dear liberals": Broad generalisation of people based on their political opinion, almost invariably done for derogatory purposes.|"lock up all the niggers": Racial slur; also refers to racial stereotyping of black people as criminals.|"deport all the wetbacks.": Racial slur; also refers to racial stereotyping of Hispanic people as illegal immigrants.|"make america great!": This phrase isn't hate speech in and of itself, but it has become very strongly correlated with other forms of hate speech.
column30: "jewkraine": Using "jew" in a derogatory manner.|"jewnited snakes": Using "jew" in a derogatory manner; also, the word "snakes" is used here for its negative connotations.
column45: "ice cream skypes": Not sure what this is referring to, but the context makes it clear this is a derogatory slur of some sort.|"googles murdering on white people": Again, I don't know what "googles" are, but the context makes the intention clear, setting them apart from white people and referencing them as a group murdering whites.
